data.description: IGNORE DAYS ON THE MARKET. A NEW ROOF. THIS CONTEMPORARY LIGHT-FILLED HOME FEATURES 3 FINISHED LEVELS,3 BEDROOMS, 3 FULL BATHS, 1 HALF BATH, 2 CAR GARAGE & MORE 2 STORY SUNKEN LIVING ROOM WITH AN OVERLOOK FROM THE BEDROOM LEVEL, CUSTOM WINDOW DRESSING, AND PALLADIAN WINDOWS. 1ST-FLOOR LIBRARY WITH GLASS FRENCH DOORS, CROWN MOLDING, RECESS LIGHTS, AND WALL-MOUNTED TV. HARDWOOD FOYER AND DINING ROOM WITH CROWN MOLDING. THE KITCHEN HAS 42-INCH CABINETS, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, RECESS LIGHTS, AND PENDANT LIGHTS OVER THE BAR. THE FAMILY ROOM HAS FANS, CROWN MOLDING, A BURNING FIREPLACE, AND DOORS LEADING TO A SPACIOUS DECK. THE MASTER BEDROOM HAS A SITTING AREA, FAN, CROWN MOLDING, AND 2 CLOSETS. MASTER BATH HAS DUAL SINKS, SHOWER HAS SEAT, WHIRLPOOL TUB, AND CROWN MOLDING. 2 SPACIOUS BEDROOMS AND HALL BATH. LOWER LEVEL WITH REC ROOM, FULL BATH, STORAGE, AND ROOM TO GROW. THE HOME BACKS TO THE PARKLAND AND THE FRONT OF THE HOME IS VERY WELL LANDSCAPED. SELLER WILL HELP WITH CLOSING COST.
